{"tid":958693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有得賭馬?】發改委：海南要擴大體育旅遊消費 鼓勵賽馬","createTime":"2018-12-28T04:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T04:54:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58226fa6875cc9056fa784d90db00669098e1ca5","tid":958693,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"發改委公布關於印發《海南省建設國際旅遊消費中心的實施方案》的通知，支持海南省建設國際旅遊消費中心，其中，提到要擴大體育旅遊消費，當中包括賽馬活動。探索發展競猜型體育彩票和大型國際賽事即開彩票。<br />\n<br />\n涉及賽馬的是通知的第9點，擴大體育旅遊消費部份。鼓勵多種活動而當中包括賽馬，其餘活動包括沙灘運動、水上運動、航空運動、汽車摩托車運動、戶外運動等。而第9點最後一句，則是「探索發展競猜型體育彩票和大型國際賽事即開彩票。」。<br />\n<br />\n通知公布後，早前炒作海南賽馬的A股羅牛山急升近3.8%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1545968031755&amp;issue=20181228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1545968031755%26issue%3D20181228&d=eweu%2BmSeRtL8pKBwkrlkFWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ab2f10e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1545968031755%26issue%3D20181228&h=5baaa589\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1545968031755&amp;issue=20181228</a>"},{"pid":"7442121c24d5eb0eb7bf777f25870a40bb3b0055","tid":958693,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}